Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428.794,395.333)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.85,0:01:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Pat--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.31,0:01:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sign
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(925.715,291.334)}悬崖危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:37.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880.297,187.333)}悬崖危险
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就救你出来  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help you out of there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你下半身还在那下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is the rest of you down there?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下半身在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rest of me is up here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我担心死了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had me worried there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.80,0:01:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your head
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发觉这些笑声毫无逻辑可言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I find all this laughter to be highly illogical
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就别笑了  来捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's stop laughing and let's start fishing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先来捉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, you get first crack
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.08,0:02:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at them--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些优雅又坚忍的海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,these graceful stoic creatures of the deep
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这话好高深  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are some big words, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以前没听过你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never heard you use them before
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荒谬  我的词汇量正无穷扩展中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, my vocabulary is infinitely expanding
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那咱来展开我们的水母网吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's expand our jellyfish nets
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟你看  我捉到一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, buddy, I captured one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  我同样绘制了一只
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I captured one as well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(818,920)}捕 捉
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.82,0:02:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而未干扰到其娇弱的生态系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without disturbing its delicate ecosystem
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如此野蛮地利用自然是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is wrong to harness nature in such a barbaric manner
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去欣赏自然的美丽和脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us go off and admire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the beauty and fragility of nature
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  相当美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fragile
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧派大星  玩点欢乐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick, let's do something fun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否要进行统计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to run some statistics
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或是观察现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or observe phenomenon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并对上述现象作出对应的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and render hypothesis of said phenomenon?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想的更多的是跳绳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was thinking more like jumping rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者单腿赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or one-legged races
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.10,注释,,0,0,0,,[ duck-duck-hermit crab：改自儿童游戏\N"duck-duck-goose"，玩法类似于丢手绢 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者一起来玩丢寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or playing duck-duck- hermit crab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毫无欢乐之感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't feel like fun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不来点笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.27,0:03:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吉他跟水母有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between a guitar and a jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母不能弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't strum a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, look at the time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really must be going
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好希望他可以好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure hope he gets better soon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好点没  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you better, Pat?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.26,0:04:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在研究这种神奇的亚种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just studying this amazing subspecies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要让你见识什么叫亚种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you subspecies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去看章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to visit Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然工作业已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since I am finished with my work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就迎合一下你那琐碎的消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll humor you in your trivial pursuits
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无论走到哪都能认得出这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd recognize that piece anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.03,0:04:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科尼利厄斯河豚第67号  郁蓝交响曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cornelius Pufferfish's Opus 67, "Symphony in Blue"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐曲很动听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful piece
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实际演奏仍需用功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Execution needs some work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.37,0:04:32.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我建议在稍慢的第7小节处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I suggest that on the seventh bar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the adagio andante
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.66,0:04:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让降b琶音力度变为很强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you add a little fortissimo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the arpeggiated b-flat scale?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没想过要这么演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought to do it like that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是因为你很少思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that is because you rarely think
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么懂音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you know so much about music?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,创意的迸发可以提供精神上的解放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A creative outlet provides a spiritual release
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及促进形成健康的心理平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and helps facilitate a healthy mental balance
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.52,0:04:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还包括边打嗝边讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that include belch talking?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生  你的幽默甚是庸俗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants, I find your humor vulgar
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你知识这么渊博  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were so knowledgeable, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不可以当我的音乐导师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could be my musical mentor?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们从头开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's take it from the top
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现不太优秀  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so excellent, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来为你演示恰当的吹奏技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me demonstrate the proper technique
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过再三的考虑  熟能生巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On second thought, practice makes perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's begin
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  我的好小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, my good chap
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不幸的是  这首曲子仅供竖笛独奏用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately this is a solo piece for clarinet only
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one, two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己去找新导师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find yourself a new mentor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你有空了  我们去吃东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you have some free time, let's get some grub
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob, I'm afraid not
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.78,0:05:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这有一瓶全新的超多泡的泡泡水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a brand new bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of super bubbly bubble soap
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必  再次谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也许等会可以扮海盗玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe later we can play pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的海绵宝宝  没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robert, my dear, it's no use
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们渐行渐远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've just grown apart
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我们过去曾经欢乐过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know we've had fun in the past
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们无法再兼容下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we're just not compatible anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候应该分道扬镳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time we went our separate ways
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such is life
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可派大星  你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Patrick, you're my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道难以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但请你振作  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but brace up, chap
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我们将来某一天会再次重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe our paths will cross again some day
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你勿忘我  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think fondly of me, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好的朋友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Best Friend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要一点专业协助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some professional help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的全新样子可以得A+了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Pat, the new you gets an "A" plus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you, Sandra
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现你的智慧也同样饶有趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I find your intellect rather stimulating as well
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那派大星  你觉得这题要怎么解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patrick, what do you think about this problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要将某一系数的形式进行转换
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You simply change the literal term to a coefficient
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,则可通过被减数得到所求的商
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the minuend will achieve the desired quotient
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连构造最简单的哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even the simplest of mammals
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,略微思考都可以解出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could figure it out with a little thought
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那几个意思  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我仅仅是认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm merely suggesting
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种方程亟需补习  而你却无能解开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you lack the ability to solve remedial equations
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在说我傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting I'm dumb?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会用更高级的词汇来形容  就比如
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd use a more sophisticated word like
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"impaired"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看你最好该走人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'd better leave
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我仅仅是在帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to help
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才用不着你这种帮忙  大懂哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need your kind of help, Mr. Know-It-All
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢从前那个弱智的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I liked you better when you were a barnaclehead
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没想过我会失去最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd lose my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.87,0:07:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又能如何争得过天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I compete with geniuses?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我满腹经纶  却无人可以共享
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by knowledge and no one to share it with
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无人与我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one I can call friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经与我欢笑的那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's that old chap I used to run with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858.924,350)}我的朋友海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(824.193,323.333)}我的朋友派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少派大星还是我记忆中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least Patrick's my friend in my memories
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The glory days
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why have we grown apart?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须运用我所有的学识解开这问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must apply all that I know to solve this problem
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(837.551,648.667)}欢乐学
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's different?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.03,0:08:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿付出一切  让昔日好友重回身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have my old buddy back by my side again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在绑架我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're kidnapping me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(519.629,694)}好耶
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱该干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要找回欢乐  无论代价如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are going to have fun, whatever the cost may be
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我们来找回欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's have some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定能让我发觉这种活动是欢乐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you quite sure I found this activity to be fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很欢乐啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fun, huh, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢乐是何时消失的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When did the fun go away, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是在你跳下那座悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It went away when you jumped off that cliff
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头撞没之后消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and knocked your head clean off
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要重复我在那天的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to duplicate my actions from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(829.536,219.333)}悬崖危险
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.27,0:09:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,查明我变化的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ascertain the origin of my chaannge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上次能找回你的头  这次肯定也行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found your head last time, I'll find it again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在这后面  不在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not back there, not under here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if I can't find it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的无头派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor headless Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的头回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, your head is back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得哪不一样没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you feel different?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实际上毫无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quite unchanged, actually
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来再也无法一同欢乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll never have fun together again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说你上次找到了我被移除的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said you found my dislodged cranial cap last time
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你究竟是在哪里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where exactly did you find it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来是在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was right here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.32,0:10:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,若我落在这  我那断头的运动轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I landed here, the trajectory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of my dismembered skull
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,末态的位置不是那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would cause it to come to rest not there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是这  正好在原位置北面五米处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but here, exactly five meters due north
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可如果说这是你的头  那我捡到了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if that's your head, then what did I pick up over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(661.224,238)}珊瑚脑田
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚脑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brain coral
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得你变这么聪明  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder you got so smart, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的旧头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your old head
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定你要放弃知识智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give up being smart and phosisticated
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.93,0:11:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只为再当我朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be my friend again?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知识智慧无法替代友情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knowledge can never replace friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁愿当个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I prefer to be an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不只是个白痴  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not just an idiot, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're also my pal
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说话啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say something, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.52,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFD3&}海章融合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.101,458.667)\frz30.02}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:12:00.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(496.135,715.334)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(410.643,443.334)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(533.537,696.667)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(429.344,542)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168.831,283.333)}我爱章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, we love you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're my favorite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是一个丑陋的工作日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for another hideous day at work
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就再忍一忍吧  帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just hang in there, gorgeous
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会在明天的竖笛独奏会上大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your star will shine at the clarinet recital tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是一个超棒的工作日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for another glorious day at work
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今早是不是很美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And isn't it a lovely morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上班路上干嘛吹竖笛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you playing the clarinet on your way to work?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.41,0:12:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在给我的竖笛演奏会练习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm practicing for my clarinet recital
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上  整个裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon all of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.54,0:13:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认出我这才子  那就是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will recognize the talent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, SpongeBoob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at the Krusty Krab, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.09,0:13:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey Sandy--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是我新做的物质瞬移器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this here's my new matter transporter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把东西转移到别处去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can move things from one place to another
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间只要一眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the blink of an eye
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着高大上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你示范下用法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how it works
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:20.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.8\pos(463.526,299.333)}瞬移器遥控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:20.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.8\pos(466.198,550)}返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:20.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.8\pos(714.658,408.667)}前进
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到哪就到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just where you think it would be
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的机器能把我传送到蟹堡王去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think your machine could zap me over to the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直很想来个生物来做实验的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always did want to try a critter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  有啥不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  感觉好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Sandy, this sure feels
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we go again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Thkwidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意咋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on with this thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太清楚这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what it is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像有点不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but something seems different about me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在拿我手干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What're you doing with my hand?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.39,0:14:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在拿你手干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what am I doing with your hand?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们融合在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all mixed up together
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明天还有竖笛演奏会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have my clarinet recital tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题不大  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.58,0:14:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下能当好兄弟  同甘共苦一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we can be best buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and do everything together forever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  都是你搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, was this your doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得把我们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to get us separated
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想知道怎么分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I wish I knew how
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你也得做点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to do something
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能跟他粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stay stuck to him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道把你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what would happen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用瞬移器传回去会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I tried zapping you back in the transporter?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good idea--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's do it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就碰碰运气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here goes nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808.163,440.667)}裤头村小学
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们  今天是提米的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, children, today is Timmy's birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what that means--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  提米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ready, Timmy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  史密斯太太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mrs. Smith
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你生下了一名健康的男婴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gave birth to a healthy baby boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能看我宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I see my baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.20,0:15:43.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一眼看到你  就深深地爱上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever since I first laid my eye on you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝  你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, baby, what's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're still the same
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a darn shame
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在设计一样全新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was working on the blueprints for a new invention
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还在雏形阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's still in the embryonic stage
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try anything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能这样子去参加竖笛演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot go to my clarinet recital like this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会继续研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll continue working on it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,期间你们要乐观点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you boys keep your heads up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Together forever
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Misery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  就没人教过你骑自行车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hasn't anybody taught you how to ride a bike?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  会好好开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll drive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(629.165,467.333)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040.594,712.667)}辣酱
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得戒了辣酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to lay off the hot sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里面到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in blazes is going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个无所事事的在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing laying around?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.96,0:16:46.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快工作去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:46.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you say so
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好你们的工作就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just go do your jobs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就非要乐于助人当小丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have to be such an accommodating buffoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  众所周知我是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, everybody knows I'm a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不像气球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I look nothing like a balloon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.96,注释,,0,0,0,,[ buffoon（小丑）与 ballon（气球）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没空扯这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去管收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to man the cash register
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554.36,208.667)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能来两份蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get two Krabby Patties, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来两份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I need two Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份蟹黄堡马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two Krabby Patties coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't reach the bun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这是在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's the hold up?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间就是金钱  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time is money, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间就是金钱  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time is money, right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, bun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们总算见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at last we meet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们破坏我生意  我都快亏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't afford you jeopardizing my business
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是成事不足败事有余
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two are more trouble than you're worth
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.76,0:17:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没把这问题解决就不准回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't come back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until you get this problem sorted out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  从好的方面看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我们还有彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least we still have each other
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们一开始才那样陷入这番窘境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how we got in this predicament in the first place
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You imbecile
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.95,0:18:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先失陪一下  我要静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me, I'd like a moment of peace
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷啊  怪咖老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock on, freaky bro
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说你已经想到分开我们的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please tell me you've figured out a way to separate us
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟分子分离射线枪打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to the molecular separator ray
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1013.878,640.667)}分子分离射线枪
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  分子分离射线枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, molecular separator ray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开始干正事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get on with it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明晚就是我竖笛演奏会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My clarinet recital is tomorrow night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我还没有完全做好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not quite done with it yet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在组装它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still putting it together
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最快的话我会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At best I'll have it ready
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后天弄好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day a2fter tomorrow maybe?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要到后天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明天还有演出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a performance tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能粘着那个黄色怪咖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't be stuck to that yellow freak
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, please--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要在演奏会之前就做好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got to do it before the show
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你明天上台之前我就做好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have it ready before you go on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(813.506,371.333)}活动中心隆重介绍\N章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  我上不了台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it, I can't go out there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一刻属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is your moment
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会塑造传说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the story you will tell
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待到你再回忆此刻  你已成为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you look back as a
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,superstar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Superstar?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上台给他们瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go out there and give them
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们所看过的最好表演
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the best darned show they've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表演必须继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the show must go on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先鱼们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlefish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村社区活动中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's community rec center
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隆重介绍  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is proud to present Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老公  我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey, I'm scared
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷啊  怪咖老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock on, freaky bro
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们真的好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They really liked it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.28,0:20:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在喝彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they're cheering
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Superstardom--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this must be what it feels like
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这种模样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what it looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sounds like
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.04,0:21:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what it smells like
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直让我陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Simply intoxicating
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there you boys are
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我正好及时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分子分离射线枪这么一射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One blast of this molecular separator ray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就能永久分离了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll be separated for good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.19,0:21:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no wait--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.26,0:21:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  先别射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to be sick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老子要走人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.16,0:21:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这么个名气时刻没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My one moment of fame gone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有什么办法可以倒回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some way to reverse this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱碰  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是非常敏感的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a very sensitive device
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我不会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I wouldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你有什么毛病  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what seems to be the problem, Mr. Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生下来就有这毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all started when I was born
